                "BTTScriptType": 3,
                "BTTAppleScriptString": "tell application \"QuickTime Player\"\n    if (exists document 1) then\n        set docRef to document 1\n        set newRate to (rate of docRef) + 0.5\n        if newRate > 4.0 then set newRate to 4.0\n        set rate of docRef to newRate\n    end if\nend tell",
